♪♪　この腕に感じたい　your soul

13
00:00:56,690 --> 00:00:59,700
♪♪　This moment I can feel
前兆到来を知る

14
00:00:59,700 --> 00:01:02,630
♪♪　このままいくぜ
I’m The Noizy Tribe

15
00:01:02,630 --> 00:01:05,400
♪♪　Come with me,
come and cry with me

16
